  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/b45360d34c7fba542c4f51645c5c6c59.poster.avif?t=1738317609\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/b45360d34c7fba542c4f51645c5c6c59.webm?t=1738317609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/b45360d34c7fba542c4f51645c5c6c59.mp4?t=1738317609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Set sail in Rum N’ Gold, a naval Battle Royale action that takes you back to the age of sail. With tactical combat, ship customization, and a relentless storm, every round is a thrilling adventure!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DYNAMIC SAILSHIP COMBAT</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/58a42fc4a963ba29fe92ba7622458b12.poster.avif?t=1738317609\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/58a42fc4a963ba29fe92ba7622458b12.webm?t=1738317609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/58a42fc4a963ba29fe92ba7622458b12.mp4?t=1738317609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Engage in tactical battles on the high seas. Anticipate enemy moves, pick your shot, unleash your cannons, and dodge the return fire.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZE YOUR SHIP</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/ecffe07d9d4b6eabbedd4174bceb0ccb.poster.avif?t=1738317609\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/ecffe07d9d4b6eabbedd4174bceb0ccb.webm?t=1738317609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/ecffe07d9d4b6eabbedd4174bceb0ccb.mp4?t=1738317609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unlock a variety of ships and customize their appearance. Each ship has its own strengths and weaknesses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE THE STORM</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/e8d7ac0129c862874e60dd0317f291cf.poster.avif?t=1738317609\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/e8d7ac0129c862874e60dd0317f291cf.webm?t=1738317609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/e8d7ac0129c862874e60dd0317f291cf.mp4?t=1738317609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The dark storm surrounds you while you engage the enemy. You’ll need to navigate carefully to avoid getting caught in it and be hit by other obstacles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHALLENGE YOUR FRIENDS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/c0febd86bb68a5c206b4cdac11902ce6.poster.avif?t=1738317609\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/c0febd86bb68a5c206b4cdac11902ce6.webm?t=1738317609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881600/extras/c0febd86bb68a5c206b4cdac11902ce6.mp4?t=1738317609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Form a fleet with your friends and compete in the same round, each for themselves, to see who is the best captain!",
